## Git safety

Always run `vault-git-snapshot.ps1` **before and after** any vault file mutation from Cursor. Never add `.git` inside the OneDrive vault folder.

Before **push**: `git --git-dir=… --work-tree=… pull --rebase origin main` (or use snapshot only after pull). Pi nightly backup also pushes to the same repo — rebasing first avoids modify/delete conflicts on files Pi still had (e.g. `safeBackup` copies).

